<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<!-- 
<link href="/assets/home.css" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" /> -->
<%=stylesheet_link_tag "home"%>
<style>
.max-page{
	background-image:url('/bg-masthead(grad).jpg');
	background-size:cover;
	height:100%;
	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	background-attachment: scroll;
	background-position: center;
}

.main_text{
	text-align: center;
	margin-top: 20%;
}

#point_button{
	margin: 0 auto;
}

#list_button{
	margin: 0 auto;
}
.navbar{
	padding-top:0px;
	padding-bottom:0px;
}

.footer{
	position: relative;
	display: block;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0 0 60px;
	background: #f7f7f7;
	text-align: center;
}

@media (max-width:1023px){
	.max-page{
		background-image:url('/ipad_main.png');
	background-size:cover;
	height:100%;
	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	background-attachment: scroll;
	background-position: center;
	}
	.navbar{
		padding-top:0px;
		padding-bottom:0px;
	}
	.main_text{
		font-size: 180%;
	}
	
	#point_button, #list_button, .file_upload_link, .badge{
		margin-top: 10%;
	}

	.container{
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

}

</style>
</head>
<body>


<div style="display:flex" class="max-page">
	<div class="main_section">
		<div class="main_text">
		<h1 class="font-weight-bold" id="main_text">인쇄물 예약하고,<br>대기없이 픽업하자!</h1><br><br>
          <h2 id="main_text">프린트 테이크아웃 서비스<br><strong>"뽀바드림"</strong></h2>
      	</div>
		<div class="file_upload">
			
			<div class="file_upload_link">
				<a href="/home/fileupload">
					<button class="custom-button">
						파일업로드
					</button>
				</a>
			</div>
		
		</div>

		<div class="list_point">
			<div class="filecurrent_li">
				<a href="/home/filecurrent"><img src='/list_btn.png' height="35%" id="list_button">
					<span class="badge badge-danger"><%= @count %></span></a>
			</div>
			<div class="point">
				<a href="/payment/cashflow"><img src='/point_btn.png' height="35%" id="point_button"></a>
			</div>
		</div>


	</div>

	</div>
</div>


</body>

<footer>
	<div class="contact">
		<p>문의사항은 bbobadream1004@gmail.com으로 보내주세요!</p>
	</div>
</footer>
</html>


